## üì• Installation

### Manual Installation
1. Download the release files below (main.js, manifest.json, styles.css)
2. Create folder: `VaultFolder/.obsidian/plugins/canvasgrid-transit/`
3. Copy the 3 files to this folder
4. Restart Obsidian and enable the plugin in Settings > Community Plugins

### BRAT Plugin
1. Install BRAT plugin in Obsidian
2. Add repository: `zhuzhige123/Canvasgrid-Transit`
3. Enable in Community Plugins

